                    <p class="editable" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #ffffff;">Giving directly to nonprofits furthers critical missions. <a href="/nonprofits/" style="color: var(--cftv-gold);">Nonprofits</a> receive 100% of your donation.</p>
                    <a href="https://cfjh.iphiview.com/cfjh/Fundholders/AccountInformation/tabid/495/dispatch/accountselection_id$10906_hash$1c0c71b9a8078a604dbdfa2c94b19b5566a479d2/Default.aspx" class="thm-btn cta-banner__btn" style="margin-top: auto; align-self: flex-end;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Give Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Become a Challenger -->
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="give-option-card" style="background: var(--cftv-navy); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <div class="give-option-icon" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        <i class="fa fa-users" style="font-size: 48px; color: var(--cftv-gold);"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="editable" style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Become a Challenger</h2>
                    <p class="editable" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #ffffff;"><a href="/challengers/" style="color: var(--cftv-gold);">Challengers</a> help sustain the local nonprofit community by offering matching funds to all participating organizations during the Tin Cup Challenge, supporting Competitive Grants, funding Youth Philanthropy initiatives, and contributing to Nonprofit Resources like workshops at the Community Foundation of Teton Valley.</p>
                    <a href="https://cfjh.iphiview.com/cfjh/Fundholders/AccountInformation/tabid/495/dispatch/accountselection_id$11252_hash$6aeb294b414a6f27714f431e8e964f245b3411bf/Default.aspx" class="thm-btn cta-banner__btn" style="align-self: flex-end;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Become a Challenger</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Why Both Matter -->
        <div class="section-title text-center" style="margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <span class="section-title__tagline editable">The Power of Giving Together</span>
