                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="editable" style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin-bottom: 10px;">Direct Gifts</h3>
                        <p class="editable" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin: 0;">When people give directly, nonprofits raise critical support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div style="background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 35px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;">
                    <div style="flex-shrink: 0;">
                        <div style="width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--cftv-gold); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                            <i class="fa fa-users" style="font-size: 24px; color: var(--cftv-navy);"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="editable" style="font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin-bottom: 10px;">Challenger Match</h3>
                        <p class="editable" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin: 0;">When Challengers fuel the match, every dollar goes further.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 20px; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
            <p class="editable" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--cftv-navy); margin-bottom: 10px;">These two ways of giving work together to strengthen our nonprofit community with more funds, more confidence, and greater stability. Keep the momentum growing and Teton Valley thriving - give today!</p>
            <p class="editable" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--cftv-navy); opacity: 0.8;">Give online, by check, wire, or stock. The Community Foundation stewards your gift and provides one tax receipt.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

